  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "09e1b89cea8bff360b9de9ef92d2ad334cc3916c85051ef9b579a9e802a44c2d": "Good work, [?]! At last we can relax. We've completed our task and you have done me a great service!",
    "2b134fd8799c90bb321e6bef7760b8aadc65289b73859305f61098074085414c": "Great work, [?]. Now, I have something for you, but you're going to need a space in your inventory. Speak to me again when you have made some room.",
    "32583053017f41689029140a6759122ba0ba78d1de0e56a047adc784a509c6e7": "I told you, [?]. It is for my collection of magical items and trinkets, weird and wonderful thereof.",
    "3a52d85231a14f8b1446bf023d553452c5fbc667001f7e629e33f9c53568276c": "I'm sure it was meant to be! Don't worry, [?], you'll be fine. Now was there anything else?",
    "5084218108839353f773a5ef32529ba315fba7a7e94b72d19b20260d540effb1": "Excellent, [?]! I'll take that as well. I hope all this work wasn't too difficult.",
    "5ee544fc836110d06084ed80c03a1431b6c926991b838e00563f1d59643780c1": "Not to worry, [?] Go and speak to Rupert. These items have a strange way of returning to their owners sometimes!",
    "741c8cd172fcb5eb1b97adc232185c05d778c6e151153a50ec709bfd9e4d210d": "You must plant them in the ground. Water them well. Then the magic will work, it's...er...magic...yes! Plant them, [?].",
    "86ab1c2d16f7a998ea9fc06aa5e2ff4c921baebbb334140ac6815d9437f593bc": "Well it just so happens, [?], that I have something you simply must have!",
    "cba71566dfc8fde008720eb6c1b80f58f753de7a6f1ffaf2551bb1646638c2f9": "But although this task should be easy, you must be careful [?]. Grimgnash has a very bad temper and even sharper claws!",
    "d9c9dded61e0a4030e9707b98391ec42582347d7f33c55457991c4642eb7ebb2": "Ahhh, but not beans like this, young [?]. No, not at all! These are 'magic' beans.",
    "f88473dcbaaf3feb4ee1c3728f5f97e357ad5aa67f92bef60add01804f6187f6": "Ah, [?]! Good to see you again."
  }
}